5.0 Payment of compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Privatsikring's ordinary means of payment is by bank
transfer. Privatsikring therefore requires details of the
relevant bank and account number in order to be able to pay compensation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, compensation may be paid by check on payment of a fee that
will be deducted from the compensation paid.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Compensation sums payable to children under the age of 18 will be paid in
accordance with the provisions concerning funds for minors.
