6.0 Transfer of rights/recourse
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
It is not permitted to mortgage or transfer rights pursuant to this
coverage without the express consent of Privatsikring. If payments are
made from the coverage, Privatsikring is to enter into the insured's
rights.
