9.0 Danish Insurance Complaints Board
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Privatsikring is affiliated with the Danish Insurance Complaints Board.
.br
In the event of disagreement between the insured and Privatsikring
concerning the insurance coverage and renewed contact with Privatsikring
fails to produce a satisfactory result for the insured, the insured is
entitled to complain to:
